longBusinessSummary: GMV Minerals Inc., an exploration stage company, engages in the sourcing and exploration of mineral properties in Arizona, the United States. The company primarily explores for gold deposits. It holds a 100% interest in the Mexican Hat Gold Project consisting of 40 unpatented lode mining claims covering an area of approximately 4,800 acres located in Cochise County, Arizona. The company was formerly known as Goldmember Minerals Inc. and changed its name to GMV Minerals Inc. in March 2008. GMV Minerals Inc. was incorporated in 2006 and is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
